00:36:59,340 --> 00:37:00,410
Thank you.

547
00:37:01,370 --> 00:37:02,250
I'll be right back.

548
00:37:19,210 --> 00:37:20,710
Seeing a psychiatrist

549
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:22,140
is not a big deal.

550
00:37:22,420 --> 00:37:24,640
It's just like talking
to a hole in a tree.

551
00:37:25,860 --> 00:37:26,790
Let me tell you this.

552
00:37:26,870 --> 00:37:27,860
Human brains are

553
00:37:27,950 --> 00:37:29,940
just like a container

554
00:37:30,030 --> 00:37:31,820
filled with different emotions.

555
00:37:31,910 --> 00:37:34,170
Sometimes, you'll have to empty it out.

556
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:36,030
If you don't,

557
00:37:37,940 --> 00:37:39,770
it will explode.

558
00:37:42,660 --> 00:37:43,540
I'm getting off now.

559
00:37:47,850 --> 00:37:49,510
Liang Mu Ze,
you must attend the appointment.

560
00:37:49,690 --> 00:37:50,670
You must.

561
00:37:53,390 --> 00:37:54,890
You really must.

562
00:38:00,030 --> 00:38:01,690
Make way please.

563
00:38:02,170 --> 00:38:03,230
Xia Chu?

564
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:04,670
Xia Chu.

565
00:38:04,900 --> 00:38:05,780
Mi Gu.

566
00:38:05,990 --> 00:38:07,250
-Xia Chu.
-Mi Gu.

567
00:38:08,010 --> 00:38:08,990
Xia Chu.

568
00:38:09,100 --> 00:38:10,200
Mi...

569
00:38:15,430 --> 00:38:17,050
-Zhuo Ran is in the emergency room.
-What?

570
00:38:17,140 --> 00:38:18,680
Zhuo Ran is in the emergency room.

571
00:38:35,180 --> 00:38:37,840
The radiograph of your left ventricle
and coronary artery

572
00:38:38,040 --> 00:38:39,100
shows no sign of infarction.

573
00:38:39,230 --> 00:38:41,250
We can eliminate the possibility of
myocardial infarction.

574
00:38:41,340 --> 00:38:42,850
However, we've found that

575
00:38:43,250 --> 00:38:46,590
at the apex of your heart,
most of the ventricles don't contract.

576
00:38:46,720 --> 00:38:49,940
From the radiography, a swollen ventricle
that looked like a wilting octopus is seen

577
00:38:50,100 --> 00:38:52,640
and the markers of myocardial damage

578
00:38:53,070 --> 00:38:54,370
has started to increase.

579
00:38:55,040 --> 00:38:56,140
It means

580
00:38:57,320 --> 00:38:58,550
death of heart muscles.

581
00:38:59,870 --> 00:39:01,250
Judging by your current condition,

582
00:39:01,350 --> 00:39:03,810
I can say that the dizziness

583
00:39:04,030 --> 00:39:05,970
and chest-pain is all due to

584
00:39:06,510 --> 00:39:08,500
stress cardiomyopathy.

585
00:39:08,590 --> 00:39:09,900
Stress cardiomyopathy?

586
00:39:12,480 --> 00:39:13,730
You've always been healthy.

587
00:39:13,820 --> 00:39:15,140
You even wanted to
get into a military school.

588
00:39:15,230 --> 00:39:16,770
How can you have stress cardiomyopathy?

589
00:39:19,660 --> 00:39:20,540
Xia Chu.

590
00:39:22,570 --> 00:39:23,820
This condition

591
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,080
is usually caused by

592
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:27,520
intense emotional or physical stress.

593
00:39:27,610 --> 00:39:28,660
For example,

594
00:39:29,080 --> 00:39:30,030
a shock,

595
00:39:30,710 --> 00:39:31,490
deep fear

596
00:39:31,590 --> 00:39:33,770
or a sudden loss of a loved one

597
00:39:34,050 --> 00:39:35,390
which can cause an epilepsy attack.

598
00:39:37,670 --> 00:39:39,450
In your case, it's because
of a phone call.

599
00:39:44,580 --> 00:39:45,880
I want to talk to Xia Chu

600
00:39:46,250 --> 00:39:47,270
in private.

601
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:49,540
No problem.

602
00:39:51,600 --> 00:39:52,700
Don't get worked up.

603
00:39:55,230 --> 00:39:55,990
Do your ward rounds

604
00:39:56,070 --> 00:39:57,690
-20 minutes later.
-Yes.

605
00:40:05,740 --> 00:40:06,770
Liang Mu Ze.

606
00:40:08,590 --> 00:40:09,570
Why are you here?

607
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:10,810
I'm looking for someone.

608
00:40:10,900 --> 00:40:11,740
Is it Zhuo Ran?

609
00:40:11,830 --> 00:40:12,730
No, Xia Chu.

610
00:40:13,540 --> 00:40:15,400
Why is everyone asking for her today?

611
00:40:15,690 --> 00:40:17,120
-Who else did?
-Director Zhang.

612
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:18,770
I just got a call
from Cardio Surgery Department.

613
00:40:18,860 --> 00:40:20,700
They need you to check on ward 18.

614
00:40:20,790 --> 00:40:21,310
Alright, I got it.

615
00:40:21,390 --> 00:40:22,530
I'll get back to work now.

616
00:40:25,460 --> 00:40:26,490
She is in that ward.

617
00:40:26,620 --> 00:40:27,520
Go on.

618
00:40:38,470 --> 00:40:39,730
I met Mi Gu just now.

619
00:40:39,890 --> 00:40:41,380
She told me you're in the hospital.

620
00:40:44,300 --> 00:40:45,560
She sent you here?

621
00:40:46,040 --> 00:40:47,550
You were together last night?

622
00:40:48,330 --> 00:40:50,630
What's with the phone call?

623
00:40:57,460 --> 00:40:59,080
You have to tell me, Zhuo Ran.

624
00:40:59,420 --> 00:41:00,600
What did you call me just now?

625
00:41:00,880 --> 00:41:01,860
Zhuo Ran.

626
00:41:02,170 --> 00:41:03,500
You still remember this person,

627
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:05,240
don't you?

628
00:41:10,060 --> 00:41:11,160
Of course I do.

629
00:41:14,100 --> 00:41:15,290
What are you saying?

630
00:41:16,470 --> 00:41:17,450
You do remember.

631
00:41:18,050 --> 00:41:19,030
You should also remember

632
00:41:20,260 --> 00:41:22,650
those weekends you spent together,

633
00:41:23,420 --> 00:41:25,280
those detective novels you read together,

634
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,450
the path you took together after school,

635
00:41:28,590 --> 00:41:29,810
that bottle of water,

636
00:41:30,470 --> 00:41:31,530
that diary

637
00:41:31,950 --> 00:41:33,450
and the never-ending letters
you wrote each other.

638
00:41:33,590 --> 00:41:34,610
All those memories

639
00:41:34,860 --> 00:41:36,600
were your past with Zhuo Ran.

640
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:37,680
It's Zhuo Ran.

641
00:41:37,830 --> 00:41:39,010
Xia Chu, it's Zhuo Ran.

642
00:41:39,270 --> 00:41:40,150
It's Zhuo Ran.

643
00:41:40,730 --> 00:41:41,650
Calm down, Zhuo Ran.

644
00:41:41,750 --> 00:41:42,770
-You can't get up...
-This.

645
00:41:43,780 --> 00:41:44,660
This part of me

646
00:41:44,760 --> 00:41:45,640
almost stopped beating

647
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:48,020
just now.

648
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:49,130
It's because

649
00:41:50,830 --> 00:41:51,860
I was sad

650
00:41:52,260 --> 00:41:53,960
that you forgot Zhuo Ran.

651
00:42:02,590 --> 00:42:04,860
I need to do my ward rounds now.
I'll visit you later.

652
00:42:05,740 --> 00:42:06,960
That comrade...

653
00:42:12,830 --> 00:42:14,170
Don't be with him.

654
00:42:19,070 --> 00:42:20,580
Are you kidding me?

655
00:42:21,150 --> 00:42:22,610
It can't be him.

656
00:42:31,150 --> 00:42:32,880
Anyone can misunderstand
my relationship with him,

657
00:42:33,860 --> 00:42:35,170
but not you.

658
00:42:36,420 --> 00:42:37,960
For a very long time,

659
00:42:38,160 --> 00:42:39,490
I can't even stand
hearing the words,

660
00:42:39,590 --> 00:42:40,610
special force.

661
00:42:41,070 --> 00:42:42,320
Let alone getting into a relationship.

662
00:42:45,150 --> 00:42:46,640
You should know the reason.

663
00:43:01,040 --> 00:43:02,100
Xia Chu.

664
00:43:03,490 --> 00:43:04,510
Why are you here?

665
00:43:08,720 --> 00:43:09,900
It was in the car?

666
00:43:10,740 --> 00:43:11,840
I'm so forgetful.

667
00:43:12,030 --> 00:43:13,530
Sorry for causing you trouble.

668
00:43:13,930 --> 00:43:14,990
Thank you.

669
00:43:17,600 --> 00:43:18,830
Where are you going?

670
00:43:18,920 --> 00:43:19,710
I'm going to visit Xiao Jun.

671
00:43:19,800 --> 00:43:21,290
Have you seen the psychiatrist?

672
00:43:22,710 --> 00:43:24,010
I am talking to you.

673
00:43:24,520 --> 00:43:25,980
-No, I didn't.
-Why?

674
00:43:26,310 --> 00:43:27,330
I don't want to.

675
00:43:28,200 --> 00:43:30,210
Liang Mu Ze,
do you still want the photo?

676
00:43:31,780 --> 00:43:32,770
It's up to you.

677
00:43:49,510 --> 00:43:50,680
<i>Where are you?</i>

